      "example_rewrite": "Replace generic rows with actionable Story Portal specifics: | **Issue** | **Story Portal Context** | **CSS Response Protocol** | | Recording failure mid-session | Story Portal records in .sp3 format; failures most commonly occur due to Bluetooth microphone dropout or background app interruption on iOS 16 | Ask: device model, OS version, microphone type. Send KB-CSS-REC-04 (Bluetooth recording recovery guide). If session file partially saved, escalate to TSE with session ID — partial recovery may be possible. | | Festival recording loss | During live festivals, server sync delays up to 90 seconds are expected and do not indicate data loss | Do NOT tell user recording is lost until TSE confirms. Send holding message: 'Your recording may still be processing — please wait 5 minutes before retrying.' | | Emotional distress about lost story | User may have recorded a deceased family member or a one-time event | Lead with: 'I understand how important this recording is. Let me do everything I can to recover it.' Escalate immediately to TSE Priority queue — do not troubleshoot further at Tier 1. |"
